  <sect2>
    <title>Component Description</title>
    <para>This component reads soil information from an ASCII file identified by <emphasis
        role="italic">stFileName</emphasis>. For each entity from the list <emphasis role="italic"
        >hrus</emphasis> it selects the soil type identified by its attribute
        <ns:emphasis>soilID</ns:emphasis> and adds the related soil information to the entity's
      attribute set.An example of a hydrogeological parameter file is shown in  <xref
        xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"
        linkend="org.unijena.j2k.io.StandardSoilParaReader_en_fig1" xrefstyle="select: label"
      />.</para>
    <figure xml:id="org.unijena.j2k.io.StandardSoilParaReader_en_fig1">
      <title>Excerpt from an example ASCII file with soil information</title>
      <mediaobject>
        <imageobject>
